      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook the braised red cabbage</strong></p>\n<p>Heat a pot (with a lid) with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a low heat.</p>\n<p>Once melted, add the <strong>grated red cabbage</strong>,<strong> sultanas </strong>and <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>.</p>\n<p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>.</p>\n<p>Add 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml] </span><strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 45 minutes, stirring occasionally.</p>\n<p> </p>",
